sections.title: Verse 3
sections.content:
F#m      D        A      E

      F#m     D         Bm     F#m

     Bm     A  E        F#m     E

     F#m     D        A          E
Come fill to me the parting glass
     F#m       D           A         E
Goodnight and joy be with you all
     F#m       D      Bm       F#m
Goodnight and joy be with you all
